import React from 'react'
import { observer } from "mobx-react-lite";
import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container'
import Nav from 'react-bootstrap/Nav'
import Navbar from 'react-bootstrap/Navbar'
import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button'

const AppGuide = observer(() => {
    return (
        <Navbar className='guide' bg="light">
            <Container>
                <Navbar.Text><div className='node-start'/>Start Node</Navbar.Text>
                <Navbar.Text><div className='node-end'/>Target Node</Navbar.Text>
                <Navbar.Text><div className='node'/>Unvisited Node</Navbar.Text>
                <Navbar.Text><div />Visited Node</Navbar.Text>
                <Navbar.Text><div />Shortest-path Node</Navbar.Text>
                <Navbar.Text><div className='node-wall'/>Wall Node</Navbar.Text>
            </Container>
        </Navbar>
    )
})

export default AppGuide
